Commentary Text: Mukesh Kumar to Kohli, out Caught by Khaleel Ahmed!! Kohli has found short fine-leg. 3-4 juggles and Khaleel hangs on. Full on leg-stump, flicked to Khaleel who is eager and tries to grab at it, the ball dances on top of his thumb and fingers, finally after so many juggles - too many to count - he hangs on much to his relief. Good knock but could Kohli have gone a bit harder? Kohli c Khaleel Ahmed b Mukesh Kumar 55(46) [4s-5]

Commentary Text: Harshal Patel to Mitchell Marsh, out Caught by Lomror!! Lucky breakthough!! This was a knee high full toss on the pads, 9/10 times that ball would have ended beyond deep backward square leg into the stands. But Marsh miscues his flick and Lomror runs in to complete a fine take. Big wicket for RCB, a way back in the game? Mitchell Marsh c Lomror b Harshal Patel 26(17) [4s-3 6s-1]
